it.unipr.netsec.nemo.routing.ospf

Class OspfRouting

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unipr.netsec.nemo.routing.ospf.OspfRouting
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DynamicRouting

    public class OspfRouting
extends java.lang.Object
implements DynamicRouting
    Lite implementation of the OSPF protocol.

    It use Link-State (LS) flooding for distributing OSPF LS updates of all routers and computing the resulting network graph. The routing table is computed from the network graph by applying a SPF (shortest Path First) algorithm. By default, the Dijkstra algorithm is used.
